{"id": "holcim-2026-04-28-028", "date": "2026-04-28", "time_tags": {"year": 2026, "quarter": "Q2", "month": 4, "week": 18, "weekday": "Tue"}, "entities": {"companies": ["holcim"], "customers": [], "suppliers": []}, "topics": ["earnings"], "sentiment": {"label": "positive", "score": 0.5, "keywords": ["growth", "increase"]}, "importance": {"score": 0.75, "reasons": ["涉及財報"]}, "title": "Cementos Pacasmayo reports sales and earnings growth in first quarter of 2026", "content": "<p><img src=\"https://www.globalcement.com/images/news/peru-currency-1500.jpg\" /></p><p><strong>Peru</strong>: Cementos Pacasmayo, part of Holcim, reported sales of US$159m in the first quarter of 2026, up by 11% year-on-year. Earnings before interest, taxation, depreciation and amortisation (EBITDA) rose by 32% to US$50.7m. The company said that the positive results were primarily due to higher sales of cement and concrete. Net profit increased to US$23m, up by 55%, and cement volumes reached 78", "sources": [{"name": "global_cement", "url": "https://www.globalcement.com/news/20702-cementos-pacasmayo-reports-sales-and-earnings-growth-in-first-quarter-of-2026", "type": "rss"}]}
